PREAMBLE

This license governs the use, reproduction, modification, distribution, and
commercialization of Smavg 🐲 and all associated source code, documentation,
tools, agents, frameworks, APIs, plugins, examples, and derivative works
(collectively, the "Software").

Smavg 🐲 is an open project built in the spirit of open-source collaboration.
It is designed to be free for individuals, researchers, startups, companies,
and other organizations to use, modify, distribute, and build upon. When a
commercial product or service reaches meaningful scale, clear attribution to
the origin of the Software is a fair expectation.

This license is modeled after the standard MIT License with additional origin
attribution and commercial-scale attribution terms. It is intended to be
permissive: there are no royalties or fees for use under this license, and no
additional commercial-scale attribution obligation applies unless one of the
thresholds in the Commercial Scale Attribution Clause is reached.

For clarity: reaching a commercial-scale threshold does not by itself require
payment, royalties, revenue share, or a paid license. The default requirement
at commercial scale is prominent attribution. A separate commercial license is
optional and is available for organizations that want attribution-free terms,
dedicated support, legal indemnity, or custom deployment terms.

This license is not legal advice. Parties are encouraged to consult their own
counsel.

Core Values:

OPENNESS: Anyone can use, build, and ship without asking permission.
FAIRNESS: Scale creates an obligation for acknowledgment.
CLARITY: Terms should be readable without a lawyer.
FLEXIBILITY: Build your business, fork it, go your own way — just do not erase
where it came from.

